# Agent Protocol Files

## Structured environment for agents

| File            | Purpose |
|-----------------|---------|
| `auth.md`       | Authentication with vendors & payment systems |
| `llm.md`        | Prompt + logic framework for decisions |
| `guardrails.md` | Spending limits, velocity, vendor rules |
| `receipt.md`    | Standardizes invoices & metadata |
| `state.md`      | Memory layer — past approvals & preferences |

**Why?** Agents hallucinate less when context is structured.

